milestones.description: Sarfraz Nawaz has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs for PAK, going past Imran Khan's 1
This is the highest match aggregate (395) involving teams New Zealand & Pakistan in ODIs
Glenn Turner has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (14) for NZ, going past Ken Wadsworth
Asif Masood has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (7) for PAK, going past Majid Khan
New Zealand's 2-run win against Pakistan is the smallest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 22-run win against Pakistan
Zaheer Abbas has broken the record for most catches (4) in ODIs for PAK, going past Wasim Raja's 3
Wasim Raja and Javed Miandad's 22-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 14 between Pervez Mir and Javed Miandad
